17/12/2002
PODGORICA, Montenegro, Yugoslavia -- Over the weekend, authorities made several more arrests related to the sex scandal that erupted earlier this month in the republic.
Local media reported Monday (16 December) that that the operation, which started with the arrest of Deputy State Prosecutor Zoran Piperovic, has expanded to several towns.
(B92, Montenegrin Mina, BBC - 16/12/02;
Dan - 15/12/02)
